# Test API Endpoints

## Base URL
BASE_URL=http://localhost:8080
API_KEY=sailing-api-key-12345

## Health Check
GET {{BASE_URL}}/health

---

## Depart Voyage
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/voyages/depart
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ship_id": "SHIP001",
  "ship_name": "Sea Explorer",
  "departure_port": "Bangkok Port"
}

---

## Arrive Voyage
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/voyages/arrive
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "voyage_id": "replace-with-actual-voyage-id",
  "arrival_port": "Singapore Port"
}

---

## Get All Voyages
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/voyages/all?limit=10&offset=0
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}

---

## Get Voyage By ID
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/voyage/replace-with-actual-id
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}

---

## Create Checkpoint
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/checkpoints
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "voyage_id": "replace-with-actual-voyage-id",
  "location": {
    "latitude": 13.7563,
    "longitude": 100.5018
  },
  "timestamp": "2025-10-01T10:00:00Z",
  "description": "Checkpoint at Bangkok",
  "weather": {
    "temperature": 30.5,
    "wind_speed": 15.0,
    "wind_dir": 180.0,
    "wave_height": 1.5,
    "condition": "clear"
  }
}

---

## Create Checkpoints Batch
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/checkpoints/batch
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "voyage_id": "replace-with-actual-voyage-id",
    "location": {
      "latitude": 13.7563,
      "longitude": 100.5018
    },
    "timestamp": "2025-10-01T10:00:00Z",
    "description": "Checkpoint 1"
  },
  {
    "voyage_id": "replace-with-actual-voyage-id",
    "location": {
      "latitude": 13.8563,
      "longitude": 100.6018
    },
    "timestamp": "2025-10-01T11:00:00Z",
    "description": "Checkpoint 2"
  }
]

---

